name: Sydney Sweeney
description:
Sydney Bernice Sweeney (born September 12, 1997) is an American actress. She first gained attention for appearing in the television series Everything Sucks!, The Handmaid's Tale. Sweeney has starred as Cassie Howard in the HBO teen drama series Euphoria since 2019 and played a sardonic teenager in The White Lotus in 2021.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Another day, another textual inversion! Ladies and gents, Sydney Sweeney. This time I made it in a different way: 8400 steps and 90 public images instead of the usual 30. I love the results, especially with close-up pics. In the future, I will try to improve the half-body output. Suggestion: do not use the face restore.

To use it:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add sydsweeney97 to your prompt;

  • Keep the Samples around 25, CFG between 8 and 9 seems to work well;
